{"tid":2237160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局發信清算罷工醫護  工會轟惹眾怒「法定權益非缺勤」","createTime":"2020-10-10T04:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T08:09:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9166759a2816db8d557dce6ec528a6727f63fdcc","tid":2237160,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/JHUPR7UDCJETPOVU2SJ2ZNEBGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FJHUPR7UDCJETPOVU2SJ2ZNEBGM%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=169a1fae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FJHUPR7UDCJETPOVU2SJ2ZNEBGM%2F&h=4cebebeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/JHUPR7UDCJETPOVU2SJ2ZNEBGM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n醫管局發信清算罷工醫護 <br />\n工會轟惹眾怒「法定權益非缺勤」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎在港爆發初期，醫管局員工陣線發起罷工促使政府封關，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局人力資源部昨日向多名罷工醫護發電郵，要求就本年2月3日至7日之間「缺勤」解釋，並於本月23日前回覆。電郵中稱，局方會按員工回覆的「缺勤」原因，決定是否採取行動跟進；若未有按時回覆，則會假定員工同意局方所指，員工在該些日子「缺勤」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9wltFRH-zXFnreIuENIvxgphimc=/1848x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KK63JPPO2NFRDHD7JHYMO7RU44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9wltFRH-zXFnreIuENIvxgphimc%3D%2F1848x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKK63JPPO2NFRDHD7JHYMO7RU44.jpg&h=9916165b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批醫護人員在港爆疫初期發起罷工，促政府封關救港。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與律師擬定回覆方式<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理劉家獻承認發信，聲稱醫管局一直以合情、合理、合法的方式，公平地處理員工缺勤問題，收到員工資料後會按照法律意見和人事條例處理，但沒有回應涉及多少名員工。食衞局副局長徐德義回應稱，政府知道疫情下，公、私營醫院醫護人員均盡忠職守照顧病人，而相關事宜醫管局管理層之前已在其他場合解釋，暫時沒有補充。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線副主席羅卓堯表示，包括工會成員在內多名員工都有收到電郵，內容大致相同。工會早前已與法律團隊擬定回覆方式，將會就局方最新的電郵進一步商討細節，內容包括重申當日行動屬於由合法工會所舉行的合法工業行動，籲同事等待工會提供範本作一致回覆。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明批評，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥局方仍不願對話<br />\n<br />\n余慧明強調，醫護早在罷工前已向上司說明罷工行動而非「缺勤」，認為醫管局發信是在扭曲罷工定義，以「缺勤」名義對付員工是毫不尊重員工合法罷工權益，若局方有誠意解決問題，早該於罷工期間公開對話，但局方至今仍不願公開對話。"},{"pid":"34149516f98826d1aba47731aa917a33e44a09d2","tid":2237160,"uid":68111,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認左改AL就係認衰仔<br />\n風聲一無咁緊實玩撚到你走"},{"pid":"ef7fcdd704d551102690a6603dcfd6f6593e0f1a","tid":2237160,"uid":194281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"下,一早就會咁既結果啦<br />\n記得仲有班友係連登開POST<br />\n話決定停止擺工<br />\n<br />\n香港人就係咁,擺幾日工跟住當冇事發生<br />\n好心同佢講後果,仲比人屌返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7aa345dc31b173baf462d6190aa4c27393a5bf","tid":2237160,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"一早已經屌柒個垃圾工會<br />\n可惜班連燈狗死攬住當寶咁"},{"pid":"a28d4db85ba11bc222c999961007426808e1b0f5","tid":2237160,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef7fcdd704d551102690a6603dcfd6f6593e0f1a","tid":2237160,"uid":194281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"下,一早就會咁既結果啦<br />\n記得仲有班友係連登開POST<br />\n話決定停止擺工<br />\n<br />\n香港人就係咁,擺幾日工跟住當冇事發生<br />\n好心同佢講後果,仲比人屌返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"根本成單野都係為左推新人參選<br />\n永遠見好就收<br />\n記得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57655ca9d3e2ba7933ba44b87efeade838393a8","tid":2237160,"uid":125727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:02:43.000Z","msg":"學教師釘牌   個個都供樓 <br />\n認次衰仔  冇下次了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54afdef6a239df84ff658541f053b2f3790bb45b","tid":2237160,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"一嘢清算曬醫護 教育 傳媒 司法界別<br />\n完全無還擊力"},{"pid":"a3a078cba1eafec832b1432f57e2a42664d6c950","tid":2237160,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54afdef6a239df84ff658541f053b2f3790bb45b","tid":2237160,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"一嘢清算曬醫護 教育 傳媒 司法界別<br />\n完全無還擊力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣咪更加令人無後顧之憂咁反抗<br />\n7婆個班底真係豬閪咁撚柒蠢"},{"pid":"5b0cbd83ac117c28e619d541439f33e864ef99e2","tid":2237160,"uid":268896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a078cba1eafec832b1432f57e2a42664d6c950","tid":2237160,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54afdef6a239df84ff658541f053b2f3790bb45b","tid":2237160,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"一嘢清算曬醫護 教育 傳媒 司法界別<br />\n完全無還擊力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣咪更加令人無後顧之憂咁反抗<br />\n7婆個班底真係豬閪咁撚柒蠢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"你見到仲有人反抗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd3bccf769c9f40892983f8d2420a5fe1d9bde9","tid":2237160,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}